author: Adela Suliman and Andy Eckardt
title: Merkel cautions this is 'beginning' of pandemic as Trump says likely virus won't return
description: Germany's Merkel cautions this is the 'beginning of the pandemic' as Trump says unlikely coronavirus will return in the fall.
content:
German Chancellor Angela Merkel on Thursday warned the battle against the coronavirus was in its early stages and that the pandemic looked set to be part of life for the long term.
